        "created_at": "2022-03-30T02:39:24.353Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Is there documentation available on the testing approach followed by RecordLayer?</p>\n<p>Besides unit and integration tests, does RecordLayer also employ simulation testing in some way? If so, I would be really interested in learning more about it.</p>",
